title: BUG: the updated user data is not returned by the put/patch api

description:
the updated user data name/job is not returned by the post api instead the old data is returned

Steps to reproduce:
1.use /api/users path and post request with payload example

{
    "name": "Marcus",
    "job": "Software Developer"
  }
2. Update the user using the put/patch request with new data

{
    "name": "Peter",
    "job": "Software Architect"
  }

Expected Result:
the new name/job should be returned

Obtained result Result:
the old user data is returned




